OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and patchy rain will
OL,6,Fclear from southern England to leave
OL,7,Fmany places dry, though breezy, with
OL,8,Fsome warm sunshine. However, it will
OL,9,Fbe cooler with blustery showers across
OL,10,Fthe north and west of Scotland and
OL,11,Fparts of Northern Ireland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will remain breezy in the
OL,14,Fnorth with patchy rain, mainly
OL,15,Faffecting the west of Scotland.
OL,16,FElsewhere there will be clear periods
OL,17,Fwith a few fog patches. A mild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
