OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FFriday looks breezy in the
OL,6,Fnorthwest with cloud and patchy
OL,7,Fdrizzle, giving way to some more
OL,8,Fpersistent rain later. Mostly fine
OL,9,Felsewhere with lighter winds and some
OL,10,Fvery warm sunshine.
